{"tid":56003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"想切腹但係冇人介錯如何是好？","createTime":"2016-12-26T22:21:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-27T03:57:54.000Z","uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"54eff4cc9f33dbafe3c4886d3249597c316f408d","tid":56003,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T22:21:47.000Z","msg":"好耐以前日本仲好興切腹嗰陣通常會有人幫切腹者介錯（斬頭）減輕痛苦<br />\n<br />\n如果冇人幫手斬頭切腹，喺天台切完即刻跳樓會唔會好啲<br />\n<br />\n利申怕痛"},{"pid":"c8370f03cee4d5fd4bcfc23e720c9db7a34515dd","tid":56003,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T23:19:00.000Z","msg":"香港地好難搵把日本武士刀"},{"pid":"b5de2e1fd57d3460810805d88989f158af9c92ef","tid":56003,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T23:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港地好難搵把日本武士刀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n豬肉刀"},{"pid":"cb84e5ee7e386d41d76d102aa4bdf0b256d56cd4","tid":56003,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T23:56:14.000Z","msg":"菜刀都唔錯，It will kill"},{"pid":"19a27f0ca4eb341cd0a8aaa6437de3520bcec216","tid":56003,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:08:29.000Z","msg":"怕痛就唔好切啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43dd2c4f2428733c6b2e09ff5d7a59e27c95f99a","tid":56003,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:14:42.000Z","msg":"咁點解唔直接跳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n巴打有咩唔開心不妨講出黎 可能呢度有人幫你呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c5d955245ea0d9f580e1bbde9169b6900a91a54","tid":56003,"uid":37931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:16:21.000Z","msg":"切完再跳咁多餘<br />\n不如直接跳<br />\n但聽人講跳樓如果唔係頭落地要十幾分鐘先會死晒<br />\n<br />\nbtw 23192688 幫到你 <br />\n巴打有咩唔開心唔好尋死住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b5001819cf501965debe6d581417091e649fa60","tid":56003,"uid":33915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:19:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>菜刀都唔錯，It will kill</blockquote><br />\ncongrats, your blade will cut"},{"pid":"c0d15da3101e1c8fb732a803da69c9f9d01514d1","tid":56003,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T00:19:19.000Z","msg":"樓主返大陸玩笨豬跳啦<br />\n有機會有事有機會冇事<br />\n有事嘅話就達成你目標<br />\n冇事嘅話你嗰刻就會後悔點解會做呢個決定"},{"pid":"53b95a3deb24f58f6312b7ccb9d80f8066dcd7b2","tid":56003,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:21:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝上面啲巴打<br />\n主要係學業同錢銀問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前讀緊asso，未必升得返上大學<br />\n我成績明明夠去留學但係又偏偏唔夠錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個心病纏繞我兩年，本來一路keep住有睇醫生，最近都好返啲<br />\n不過早幾日因為好朋友一句話終於支持唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要切腹係因為以前對自己一個承諾：「要死就要切腹死」，算係想嚇下自己唔好自殺，但係生活壓力越嚟越大，屋企人越嚟越老，爸爸因病退休，媽媽一個人在外做嘢辛苦到白頭髮都多咗，唔想再睇落去<br />\n<br />\n（不過實有人話自己慘過我跟住就會變鬥慘大賽，講真聽到呢啲係唔會令一個承受緊痛苦嘅人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b13e72d99bc981b5f37dbc9c8dc463cb7612aa6","tid":56003,"uid":35176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:25:07.000Z","msg":"原來係抑鬱症，咁真係要小心"},{"pid":"4edc17a2c525ee3b5d407e33ced9dbd06e59ce0b","tid":56003,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:29:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝上面啲巴打<br />\n主要係學業同錢銀問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前讀緊asso，未必升得返上大學<br />\n我成績明明夠去留學但係又偏偏唔夠錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個心病纏繞我兩年，本來一路keep住有睇醫生，最近都好返啲<br />\n不過早幾日因為好朋友一句話終於支持唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要切腹係因為以前對自己一個承諾：「要死就要切腹死」，算係想嚇下自己唔好自殺，但係生活壓力越嚟越大，屋企人越嚟越老，爸爸因病退休，媽媽一個人在外做嘢辛苦到白頭髮都多咗，唔想再睇落去<br />\n<br />\n（不過實有人話自己慘過我跟住就會變鬥慘大賽，講真聽到呢啲係唔會令一個承受緊痛苦嘅人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錢銀方面就真係冇辨法改變 所以唯有努力繼續捱埋個asso佢 唔好諗咁多<br />\n朋友方面就等睇下有冇機會再搞返好個關係lo 暫時有咩問題咪多啲上黎lihkg搵下啲巴打傾下lo 實有人幫你嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"320612066a48a1e79768620becb5898c256c039e","tid":56003,"uid":43213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:32:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多謝上面啲巴打<br />\n主要係學業同錢銀問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n目前讀緊asso，未必升得返上大學<br />\n我成績明明夠去留學但係又偏偏唔夠錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個心病纏繞我兩年，本來一路keep住有睇醫生，最近都好返啲<br />\n不過早幾日因為好朋友一句話終於支持唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解要切腹係因為以前對自己一個承諾：「要死就要切腹死」，算係想嚇下自己唔好自殺，但係生活壓力越嚟越大，屋企人越嚟越老，爸爸因病退休，媽媽一個人在外做嘢辛苦到白頭髮都多咗，唔想再睇落去<br />\n<br />\n（不過實有人話自己慘過我跟住就會變鬥慘大賽，講真聽到呢啲係唔會令一個承受緊痛苦嘅人好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n因為讀唔成書去死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n施主 學海無崖 雖然宜家講你未必信 或者都係唔甘心<br />\n到你將來讀到大學 你就發覺都未必係你想要既野黎<br />\n利申 磨多左幾年先入番U 覺得真係唔洗咁強求<br />\n<br />\n襯一家人仲齊齊整整 陪多啲屋企人好過啦 仲諗死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"476547b99008ca0263e80cc1ec6c9aa46037438d","tid":56003,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:34:12.000Z","msg":"另外 如果巴打咁有武士道精神嘅話就更加唔應該放棄 你又冇做錯任何野 不過做啲自己有興趣嘅野 做下運動 行下山放鬆下個人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b47c588276f054c5d7f1c1c786e6352051db8df","tid":56003,"uid":22552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:36:53.000Z","msg":"原來怨屋企無錢比你讀書 <br />\n讀得asso比你出去留學咪又係讀野雞<br />\n慳番d錢好過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9efa423275dfcd9acbb6f95ddba254049e21d0f0","tid":56003,"uid":18756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:42:57.000Z","msg":"唔想睇落去應該做d野幫輕屋企人先岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb55c7e78b3d1f2fbb4214091f83da3cac7c3a9","tid":56003,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:45:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔想睇落去應該做d野幫輕屋企人先岩喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n目前sem break，搵緊小學私補努力唔倚賴屋企"},{"pid":"321e96c04dc1fe0437582c7b76e624ee4830a201","tid":56003,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:49:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ebe44d84fdfde3aad14cf54847768089ffde84ab","tid":56003,"uid":41736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:52:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外 如果巴打咁有武士道精神嘅話就更加唔應該放棄 你又冇做錯任何野 不過做啲自己有興趣嘅野 做下運動 行下山放鬆下個人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n岩，咁有武士道就唔好屈服<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢度好多巴打會支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0ba0b0c16e0a01abc79a994a007b11b0f9aac9","tid":56003,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:54:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多謝連登巴打<br />\n雖然素未謀面，但係知道有人支持我係一件值得欣慰嘅事<br />\n<br />\n至於講風涼話嗰條友，同我朋友無咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987e92a9422d2c5c94d3e37be7043f92a9902af1","tid":56003,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-27T03:57:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hdw.la/wp-content/uploads/2016/01/%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%80%E9%95%BF%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%80%E5%A4%A9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hdw.la%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F01%2F%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%259C%2580%25E9%2595%25BF%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25A4%25A9.jpg&h=751ab3f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果有睇過呢套戲, 有場戲係切腹, 睇完都覺好痛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}